# MDCX Docker 构建忽略清单
# 减少构建上下文体积、加速构建、避免敏感文件泄露

# === 版本控制 ===
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.gitlab

# === IDE / 编辑器 ===
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === Python 缓存与虚拟环境 ===
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# === Node.js 缓存 ===
**/node_modules/
**/.npm/
**/.yarn/
**/.pnpm-store/

# === 构建产物（容器内会重新构建） ===
MDCX-Desktop/dist/
MDCX-Desktop/dist-electron/
MDCX-Desktop/release/
MDCX-Desktop/release-green/
MDCX-Server/static/assets/
MDCX-Server/static/*.js
MDCX-Server/static/*.css
# 保留 static/index.html 作为存在性标记？不，全部忽略，容器内重新构建

# === 运行时数据（不应打包进镜像） ===
MDCX-Server/data/database/
MDCX-Server/data/logs/
MDCX-Server/data/config/config.yaml
MDCX-Server/data/backups/
MDCX-Server/data/cache/
MDCX-Server/data/*.pid
MDCX-Server/data/*.lock
data/database/
data/logs/
data/backups/

# === Electron 打包产物（容器部署不需要） ===
win-unpacked/
MDCX-Desktop/release/
MDCX-Desktop/release-green/
*.exe
*.msi
*.dmg
*.AppImage
*.deb
*.rpm

# === 参考项目源码（仅用于学习，不打包） ===
.参考/
.参考/**

# === 旧副本 ===
docker-scraper/
docker-scraper.zip

# === 文档与测试 ===
**/*.md
**/CONTRIBUTING
**/LICENSE
**/changelog.*
MDCX-Server/tests/
MDCX-Server/_schema_test.py
MDCX-Server/_test_merger.py
MDCX-Desktop/scripts/qa-*.mjs

# === Windows 特定二进制（容器为 Linux） ===
MDCX-Server/ffmpeg.exe
MDCX-Server/ffplay.exe
MDCX-Server/ffprobe.exe
MDCX-Server/*.bat
MDCX-Server/start.bat
MDCX-Server/start.sh

# === 日志与调试 ===
*.log
debug.log
MDCX-Server/data/logs/*.log

# === Docker 自身文件 ===
Dockerfile*
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

# === CI/CD ===
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml
.circleci/
